item.title: Best non member pvp account?
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

To answer the original question, don’t PVP on non-member worlds; especially as a pure. It’s fruitless, and you’ll find yourself spending far more than you’ll ever make.
If you really must PVP on f2p then don’t use range if you’re going to be over 80 combat because odds are you’ll be fighting people with rune armour; this makes the fights slow and the likelihood of you killing them very slim.
